WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.964 align:middle line:90%


00:00:00.964 --> 00:00:04.820 align:middle line:90%
[WHOOSH]

00:00:04.820 --> 00:00:07.712 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:07.712 --> 00:00:08.676 align:middle line:90%


00:00:08.676 --> 00:00:10.610 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:10.610 --> 00:00:13.870 align:middle line:84%
>> An empowered daily
life takes a lot of work.

00:00:13.870 --> 00:00:18.400 align:middle line:84%
And the first priority is
that you have to really commit

00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:20.830 align:middle line:90%
to not living a wounded life.

00:00:20.830 --> 00:00:26.740 align:middle line:84%
What part of nature is devoted
to being broken and wounded?

00:00:26.740 --> 00:00:28.730 align:middle line:90%
So that's number one.

00:00:28.730 --> 00:00:34.150 align:middle line:84%
Number two is that in order to
really live an empowered life,

00:00:34.150 --> 00:00:36.860 align:middle line:84%
you have to understand
what empowered is.

00:00:36.860 --> 00:00:38.960 align:middle line:84%
It's not about
speaking your truth.

00:00:38.960 --> 00:00:42.270 align:middle line:84%
It's about learning to tell
the truth and pursue the truth.

00:00:42.270 --> 00:00:45.756 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:45.756 --> 00:00:52.730 align:middle line:90%


00:00:52.730 --> 00:00:57.470 align:middle line:84%
This is our last episode
together on "Sacred Power",

00:00:57.470 --> 00:01:02.270 align:middle line:84%
so it's going to be a little
bit more personal because I feel

00:01:02.270 --> 00:01:06.200 align:middle line:84%
like you've gotten to
know me and how I work

00:01:06.200 --> 00:01:10.980 align:middle line:84%
and where I come from and what
my inner nature is all about.

00:01:10.980 --> 00:01:14.870 align:middle line:84%
And so I thought I would
take you a little bit more

00:01:14.870 --> 00:01:20.070 align:middle line:84%
deeply into how
I would guide you

00:01:20.070 --> 00:01:24.690 align:middle line:84%
if you were with me
in my office and you

00:01:24.690 --> 00:01:30.390 align:middle line:84%
had questions like, how would
you direct me spiritually?

00:01:30.390 --> 00:01:33.650 align:middle line:84%
And so with that in
mind, I've set up

00:01:33.650 --> 00:01:37.340 align:middle line:90%
this last episode together.

00:01:37.340 --> 00:01:39.590 align:middle line:84%
One of the most
powerful sentences

00:01:39.590 --> 00:01:42.230 align:middle line:84%
I've ever read in
my life was written

00:01:42.230 --> 00:01:46.700 align:middle line:84%
by the great Catholic Trappist
writer, priest, intellectual,

00:01:46.700 --> 00:01:49.250 align:middle line:90%
Thomas Merton in 1968.

00:01:49.250 --> 00:01:52.410 align:middle line:84%
These six words grabbed
ahold of my entire life

00:01:52.410 --> 00:01:54.710 align:middle line:84%
and positioned it
right in front of me.

00:01:54.710 --> 00:01:56.400 align:middle line:10%
"This day will
never come again."

00:01:56.400 --> 00:01:58.980 align:middle line:90%


00:01:58.980 --> 00:02:02.100 align:middle line:84%
Now, we know it's such a simple
and obvious statement, maybe,

00:02:02.100 --> 00:02:04.090 align:middle line:90%
for all of you.

00:02:04.090 --> 00:02:07.742 align:middle line:84%
But that struck me as one of
the most significant truths--

00:02:07.742 --> 00:02:09.440 align:middle line:90%
and it's a prayer--

00:02:09.440 --> 00:02:12.430 align:middle line:84%
that I would ever
realize in my life.

00:02:12.430 --> 00:02:16.480 align:middle line:84%
It's a truth that I've reminded
myself of every day since.

00:02:16.480 --> 00:02:20.110 align:middle line:84%
I've written about it,
and it's made a difference

00:02:20.110 --> 00:02:21.700 align:middle line:90%
in the lives of people.

00:02:21.700 --> 00:02:27.070 align:middle line:84%
And I don't know that
Merton ever intended that.

00:02:27.070 --> 00:02:31.930 align:middle line:10%
But somehow that last
sentence in his journal

00:02:31.930 --> 00:02:34.990 align:middle line:10%
just struck me like
a bolt of lightning,

00:02:34.990 --> 00:02:36.670 align:middle line:10%
that thought that
I would never see

00:02:36.670 --> 00:02:41.320 align:middle line:10%
the same sunrise, the same
sunset, that no flower would

00:02:41.320 --> 00:02:44.470 align:middle line:10%
look the same to me,
that I would never

00:02:44.470 --> 00:02:48.190 align:middle line:10%
have the same conversation
with the same people.

00:02:48.190 --> 00:02:51.830 align:middle line:84%
This is a once in a
lifetime moment for me.

00:02:51.830 --> 00:02:55.030 align:middle line:84%
I will never see their
faces just this way again.

00:02:55.030 --> 00:02:59.730 align:middle line:84%
Everything about it
is precious to me.

00:02:59.730 --> 00:03:04.040 align:middle line:84%
And I don't know what
will come this day, what

00:03:04.040 --> 00:03:06.400 align:middle line:84%
incredible things
may happen or not.

00:03:06.400 --> 00:03:09.260 align:middle line:90%
It's become a living truth.

00:03:09.260 --> 00:03:12.390 align:middle line:90%
It's become a living prayer.

00:03:12.390 --> 00:03:18.110 align:middle line:84%
It means that I don't have time
to waste with small things.

00:03:18.110 --> 00:03:22.910 align:middle line:84%
When you think about the
value of friends and family,

00:03:22.910 --> 00:03:25.910 align:middle line:84%
you don't wait to tell
them that you love them.

00:03:25.910 --> 00:03:29.580 align:middle line:84%
You forgive them fast
and forget even faster.

00:03:29.580 --> 00:03:32.840 align:middle line:84%
I don't have time to waste
because this day, this moment,

00:03:32.840 --> 00:03:36.630 align:middle line:90%
will never, ever come again.

00:03:36.630 --> 00:03:39.420 align:middle line:84%
Deeper than that,
it's vitally important

00:03:39.420 --> 00:03:43.260 align:middle line:84%
for you to have a daily
practice for your soul

00:03:43.260 --> 00:03:46.890 align:middle line:84%
and that that daily
practice is based

00:03:46.890 --> 00:03:51.510 align:middle line:84%
upon sacred truth, sacred
truth that naturally guides

00:03:51.510 --> 00:03:56.160 align:middle line:84%
you and contributes to
the world as a structure

00:03:56.160 --> 00:03:58.610 align:middle line:90%
of holy and sacred power.

00:03:58.610 --> 00:04:01.610 align:middle line:90%
